  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 46c1e59135e319b48873d5992935a3bc, type: 3}
  description: "L\xE0o Cai l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng
    T\xE2y B\u1EAFc B\u1ED9 \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam, gi\xE1p
    bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi v\u1EDBi Trung Qu\u1ED1c. T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh
    n\xFAi cao h\xF9ng v\u0129 v\xE0 kh\xED h\u1EADu m\xE1t m\u1EBB, n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt
    v\u1EDBi c\xE1c \u0111\u1ECBa danh du l\u1ECBch nh\u01B0 Sa Pa, \u0110\u1EC9nh
    Fansipan v\xE0 N\xFAi H\xE0m R\u1ED3ng.\n\nL\xE0o Cai c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c
    s\u1EA3n n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng n\xFAi T\xE2y B\u1EAFc nh\u01B0
    Th\u1EAFng c\u1ED1, L\u1EE3n c\u1EAFp n\xE1ch v\xE0 R\u01B0\u1EE3u t\xE1o m\xE8o.\n\nV\u1EC1
    v\u0103n h\xF3a, L\xE0o Cai l\xE0 n\u01A1i sinh s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u
    d\xE2n t\u1ED9c nh\u01B0 H\u2019M\xF4ng, Dao, T\xE0y, Gi\xE1y v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n
    s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a phong ph\xFA. C\xE1c ch\u1EE3 phi\xEAn v\xF9ng cao,
    trang ph\u1EE5c truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng v\xE0 c\xE1c l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i d\xE2n gian
    th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n r\xF5 n\xE9t \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c
    s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a c\u1ED9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c v\xF9ng n\xFAi
    T\xE2y B\u1EAFc."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1/7/2025, t\u1EC9nh L\xE0o Cai v\xE0 Y\xEAn B\xE1i
    ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c s\xE1p nh\u1EADp th\xE0nh t\u1EC9nh L\xE0o Cai m\u1EDBi, v\u1EDBi
    trung t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i Y\xEAn B\xE1i, d\xE2n s\u1ED1
    tr\xEAn 1,7 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi v\xE0 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch h\u01A1n 13.250
    km\xB2. Vi\u1EC7c h\u1EE3p nh\u1EA5t n\xE0y nh\u1EB1m x\xE2y d\u1EF1ng b\u1ED9
    m\xE1y tinh g\u1ECDn, ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n v\xE0nh \u0111ai du l\u1ECBch di s\u1EA3n
    \u0111\u1ED9c \u0111\xE1o, t\u1EADn d\u1EE5ng h\u1EA1 t\u1EA7ng cao t\u1ED1c
    N\u1ED9i B\xE0i - L\xE0o Cai v\xE0 k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i c\xE1c v\xF9ng di s\u1EA3n
    T\xE2y B\u1EAFc. "
